The {{nihongo|'''Osaka Tenmangū Shrine'''|大阪天満宮|Ōsaka Tenmangū}} is a {{ill|Shinto shrine|en|Shinto shrine|WD=Q845945|lt=Shinto shrine|1=Shinto shrine}} and one of [[Tenmangū]] founded in AD 949 in {{ill|Osaka|en|Osaka|WD=Q35765|lt=Osaka|1=Osaka}}.  The [[Tenjin Festival]] is held here annually from 24 July to 25 July.

