*{{ill|Minami-morimachi Station|en|Minami-morimachi Station|WD=Q1039923|lt=Minami-morimachi Station|1=Minami-morimachi Station}} on the two lines of {{ill|Osaka Municipal Subway|en|Osaka Municipal Subway|WD=Q303026|lt=Osaka Municipal Subway|1=Osaka Metro}}.

